    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "a minor vascular event? that sounds way more serious than just dehydration lol. but u think 600mg is safe to take right now? i dont wanna mess anything up if my head is still feeling a bit heavy. also is the coffee thing actually helpful or will it just make me more jittery?",
