      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay i'll try that. honestly though i'm still feeling a bit weird. my neck feels kind of stiff too, like i cant really look down as far as usual. is that just from the stress of the headache or should i actually be worried about something like a stroke or something? i'm kinda nervous now.",
